            "weighting": "<dd>50% (5 x 10% worksheets each) </dd>",
            "due_date": "<dd><p>Worksheet 1 - WEEK 3 - 11/08/2026 5:00 pm</p>\n<p>Worksheet 2 - WEEK 5 - 26/08/2026 5:00 pm</p>\n<p>Worksheet 3 - WEEK 7 - 9/09/2026 5:00 pm</p>\n<p>Worksheet 4 - WEEK 9 - 23/09/2026 5:00 pm</p>\n<p>Worksheet 5 - WEEK 11 - 14/10/2026 5:00 pm</p>\n<p>\n</p><p>To be submitted via Turnitin every Wednesday by 5pm, except WEEK 3 (Tuesday) due to the Wednesday Public Holiday.</p></dd>",
            "learning_objectives": "L01, L02, L03, L04, L05, L06",
