            "due_date": "<dd><p> 7/08/2026 - 23/10/2026</p>\n<p>\n</p><p>WEEK 2 - WEEK 12</p>\n<p>Submit PowerPoint slide or 1 page PDF at least 24 hours prior to the student's allocated presentation date via Blackboard submission link.</p>\n<p>The student's chosen presentation week will be considered the due date and time for this assessment.</p></dd>",
